Values.MaxThreshold: maximum threshold for auto scale, above this value autoscaler will add one server to vmss
Values.MinThreshold: minimum threshold for auto scale, below this value autoscaler will remove one server to vmss
Values.SQLConnectionString: sql server connection string which holds logic for autoscale
Values.ClientId: application key in azure active directory
Values.ClientSecret: application secret in azure active directory
Values.SubscriptionId: azure subscription id which holds vmss
